{"title":"致北京","authors":["王辽生"],"dates":[{"year":1981,"month":8,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江苏新沂  王辽生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门前穿梭的人群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们比我幸运。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我，怀了毕生干渴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耗去了半个青春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才走到这高大红墙的墙根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作此忘形的一吻！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，你们此刻看见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个五十岁的儿童，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以其仅存的一点天真，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在观礼台下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起一杯冰激凌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟然珠泪纷纷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这杯冰激凌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这杯天安门下出售的冷饮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这杯振华茶食店给我的清凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我正该用来润我的生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"润我生命之车的大小轴承！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，北京！啊，天安门！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我凄凉的岁月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这儿有我的余温；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我闷热的日子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这儿有我的清荫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我窒息的瞬间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这儿有一口新氧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我离了诱人的死神；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在醒时的梦中和梦时的醒里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的魂总在天安门驰骋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说什么来路坎坷，去路迢迢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活着正为了踢踏风尘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要我车轮旋转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路洒下的就全是琴韵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰激凌来自北冰洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一口能冷透骨心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是为什么，为什么啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门下这冰激凌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烫了我的血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烫了我的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成了滚烫滚烫的冷饮！？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}